  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create an array of cosmic lights that form a wide stage, where you alone are the star. Music of your design begins to fill the area, and you begin a dazzling performance, forcing all hostile creatures within range or who would start their turns while in range to make a Charisma saving throw.</p><ul><li><p><strong>On a failure:</strong> They are entranced by your performance, their mind beginning to fight against their body when they would otherwise act normally. Each time a creature that has failed their saving throw against this jutsu would move or act, they inflict 3d6 psychic damage upon themselves that ignores damage reduction, up to twice per turn. They cannot move out of the stage willingly unless they make a Charisma saving throw as an Action, further gaining 1 rank of Charmed and becoming unable to make another attempt until the end of your next turn on a failure.</p></li></ul><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost by 3, the damage by 2d6, and the radius by 10 feet.</p>",
